subject: College Athletics
Volleyball
NCAA Volleyball Championships
lead_paragraph: U.C.L.A. swept the four-time defending national champion Penn State in the N.C.A.A. women’s regional semifinals in Lexington, Ky., 25-20, 25-22, 25-21.
